N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6053.5 - Latent fingerprint system

State Regulations

Juvenile arrest fingerprints received and processed by DCJS
will be included in the latent fingerprint system. When juvenile arrest
fingerprints are destroyed in compliance with the provisions of the Family

Court Act, such fingerprint information will also be removed from the latent
fingerprint system. Notes
